                <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">üõí E-commerce Brand: Webflow ‚Üí 10Web, +$127K Sales</h3>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-3 border-[2px] border-purple-300">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-black text-purple-600">+$127K</div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 font-semibold">12-Month Sales</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-purple-50 p-3 border-[2px] border-purple-300">
                    <div class="text-2xl font-black text-purple-600">-$355</div>
